title: obelisk_1_end
body:
Rest now
You will need your strength 
->I will rest 
    [[next_level]] 
->I'm not tired

title: obelisk_2_end
body:
It is safe now, sleep
Sleep for ten thousand dawns
->What is this place?
    A space between places
    A time between time
    Not what but why...
    ->Why?
        Sleep [[next_level]]
->I'm afraid 
    Nothing can harm you while we're together
    Close your eyes and be at peace
    ->Close eyes
        [[next_level]]

title: obelisk_3_end
body:
You grow weary
I feel it
Wake up
->How long have I been asleep? 
    Too long! [[next_level]] 
->...

title: obelisk_4_end
body:
All is lost
We are alone
->Who are you? 
    I am you
    ->Who am I?
        One who is chained to this room [[next_level]]
->...

title: obelisk_5_end
body:
Maybe now we can sleep
Peace comes for all of us
Eventually
->Sleep 
    [[next_level]]
->Stay in the Void

title: death
body:
Return to me
Death is a new beginning
[[Accept your death|restart]]

title: start
body:
Awaken my child
A bitterness disturbs us [[next_level]]
